<emphasis box="[297,576,1930,1952]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="475">Amphigymnas woodmasoni</emphasis>
(Walsh, 1891)
</taxonomicName>
. 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[743,761,1930,1951]" pageId="24" pageNumber="475">A</emphasis>
: dorsal view of specimen IE-2007-798, 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1179,1196,1931,1952]" pageId="24" pageNumber="475">B</emphasis>
: SEM view of ossicles from the body wall. Scale bars: A = 1cm; B = 50µm.
</paragraph>
</caption>
